<br>
Map the /loc command to your autoattack button. That way if you lose, at least you'll have some Idea where you were when you bit it. Also good if you get jumped by a much higher level mob and die within three spells/melee rounds or less, autoattack is more or less a reflex for me, I'm much more likely to mash that key in a hurry than type /loc or look for the social button.<br>
<br>
Just a thought<br>
